{"type": "article", "id": 2959, "title": "手机充电插座", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-21T08:20:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232838pWGkZSfhwnma6xc5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t冬天快到了，崭新的 iPhone 也已经入手了，这个时候可不要忘了给你的手机配件更新换代。近日，美国 QUELL &amp; CO 公司推出了一款充满暖暖冬日气息的手机充电底座 Spool Dock ，充电线嵌在一个金属搭配橡木地底座中，对应不同型号接口的数码设备，可以整齐地将电源线收纳其中。灰色的羊毛毡设计可谓贴心，保护手机不因摩擦而受到损坏。Spool Dock 支持 iPhone 6、 iPhone 6 plus、 iPhone 5/5S/5C以及iPad mini 和第五代iPod，定价 65 美元，<a href=\"http://www.quellandco.com/products/spool-dock\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"http://static.dezeen.com/uploads/2014/10/sq.gif\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232836mGuAZcWPa7BFSnVL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6234375\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232836gQ3WfsMHFtKNOjZm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6234375\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232837FPLYQHqfXvc57eM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6234375\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}